code: @Override protected OutputStream decorateWithCompression(NonClosingOutpusStreamDecorator stream) throws IOException {     return new SnappyFramedOutputStream(stream, COMPRESSION_BLOCK_SIZE, MIN_COMPRESSION_RATIO). }
